snippet.title: Time to Morp - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
After a year in Early Access, Time to Morp finally fully released on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/977510/Time_to_Morp/

Enjoy gameplay trailer of cozy base building game! 

Play with friends in a cozy base-building adventure! Take care of adorable creatures — Morps, explore, discover new species, grow crops, fish, build relationships with your crew, decorate your perfect home, and automate production along the way!
